title: Nourish Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Raw, Western, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little counter in the space of the previous Funky's Coffee, since July 2014. Focus is on unprocessed, organic food. Most meals are veg by default with option to add meat/dairy. Vegan choices include a vegan pizza made with cashew cheese, chia pudding with coconut yoghurt, raw chia bread stack and raw cheesecake, non-dairy milks for drinks.
